title: Cant Log In after transfer
body: I transfered my account yesterday frm Eu Nordic East and cant log in now. If i try to log in back at Eu it says my acc is transfered, but when I try to log in here nothing happens, as if my account doesnt exist. I made a ticket yesterday but still havent gotten a response. This is an old account that I have apparently

replies.body: I'm not seeing any transfers on this account, but if you shoot me the Summoner name of the account you transferred I can check up on it for you!
BUMP IT UP BOYS, SAME PROBLEM RIOT PLEASE :) Tried to swap from euw to eune on one of my acc's and i got the same problem as you, riot some attention ty : )
